I wasn\'t happy with the elven armor, it looked to dark and i wanted it to be more shiny and golden :P.
Just thought some of you would like it aswell.
descriptionHtml:
I wasn\'t happy with the elven armor, it looked to dark and i wanted it to be more shiny and golden :P.
Just thought some of you would like it aswell. 

Enjoy :D


Quite simpel to install.. 

Just drag the Data folder into the main folder of Skyrim, when a window pops up with the question if you want to combine the maps, press yes.

*Uninstal or undo: delete the map called elven... or put the \"backup_old\" version into the \"M\" folder, overwriting the new golden version.

Greetz,

PhoenixNL
author: PhoenixNL
